  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nWhen running with --weakSubjectivityLatest the node should immediately do a head sync, but it doesn't. It takes a long time to realize it's behind, then does a finalized sync and gets to the head.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nQuickly get to the head with `--weakSubjectivityLatest`\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n\r\nRun with `--weakSubjectivityLatest` on mainnet",
